@startuml
title OpenData - System Context

actor "Operator or Scheduler" as Operator
rectangle "OpenData\nCommand-Line Application" as OpenData
cloud "Open Data Provider" as Provider
database "Microsoft SQL Server" as SqlServer
folder "Source Archive" as Archive
file "Console and Log Files" as Logs

Operator --> OpenData : --plugin <id>\n[--file settings]
OpenData --> Provider : HTTPS request
Provider --> OpenData : dataset response
OpenData --> Archive : raw source,\nchecksum and metadata
OpenData --> SqlServer : validated records\nand run metadata
OpenData --> Logs : java.util.logging

@enduml
